des:
The Duux skill allows you to control your connected Duux devices with Alexa.
Monitor and control your Duux devices by using voice commands. If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us at email:service@duux.com

This new Skill is only intended for use with the latest models of Duux products (only compatible with serial numbers beginning with "22"). The Duux app will help you identify which version you can use.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap, or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Duux products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our « Duux » app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Duux account in our « Duux » app;
(3). You need to have some Duux devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Duux" app and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in « Duux » skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search « Duux (Gen 2) » skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of « Duux », and you'll be navigated to Duux login page;
(9). Input your Duux account username and password, and you'll be redirected to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the air purifier"
“Alexa, turn off the air purifier"

Keep an eye on the Duux skill as we'll be adding more features and products in the near future.
